            "product_url": "https://warmbody-coldmind.com/products/weightlifting-lether-belt?sca_ref=5120971.qSPHd7ePgJ",
            "product_rating_description": "<p>The belt was created by former Olympic weightlifter <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oleksiy_Torokhtiy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oleksiy_Torokhtiy\">Oleksiy Torokhtiy</a> in consultation with our very own international team of experts. It was made following standardized measurements familiar to both casual and competitive lifters and achieved both IPF & USAPL approval for it. It’s also a staple of many deadlift belt reviews.</p><ul><li><strong>Fastening Mechanism:</strong> Double prong belt buckle</li><li><strong>Material: </strong>Genuine leather, stainless steel</li><li><strong>Size:</strong> S, M, L, XL, 2XL, 3XL</li><li><strong>Waist Size Range:</strong> 28”-52” (72-131cm)</li><li><strong>Width:</strong> 4” </li><li><strong>Thickness:</strong> 6mm</li><li><strong>Quality Assurance: </strong>Made in Ukraine, IPF & USAPL approved</li></ul>",
