            "product_pros": "<ul><li>Nylon belts are more mobile and flexible than leather</li><li>Unique design (with even more options)</li><li>Velcro closure can be adjusted to the exact fit</li><li>Large size range</li><li>Patches can be added for even more customization</li></ul>",
            "product_cons": "<ul><li>Nylon is not as durable as leather</li><li>Velcro closure tends to give out faster than a metal buckle or lever</li></ul>"
