            "half_width_review_image": true,
            "product_review_image_caption": "<p>Photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Cn14Ff5uCOL/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Cn14Ff5uCOL/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\">@element26.co</a></p>",
            "product_text_content_2": "<p>However, the durability of the belt is tied to the nylon integrity. If the fastening system gives in first, there’s no official way to replace it other than coming up with a DIY solution. This can result in a somewhat unsatisfying purchase since the leather itself is quite good and will last.</p>",
